+/*
+ *	MPTCP implementation - Linked Increase congestion control Algorithm (LIA)
+ *
+ *	Initial Design & Implementation:
+ *	Sébastien Barré <sebastien.barre@uclouvain.be>
+ *
+ *	Current Maintainer & Author:
